I'm earning less than you.

1015
00:43:16,020 --> 00:43:16,690
That'll solve it.

1016
00:43:17,210 --> 00:43:19,340
Of course I won't tell others. Why would I?

1017
00:43:20,210 --> 00:43:20,940
It's fine then.

1018
00:43:21,540 --> 00:43:22,460
I'll do it.

